Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.04,0:01:08.56,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,This is Mr Mathison. He's a doctor.\N{\rCHT}這是馬先生 他是醫生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.04,0:01:11.77,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Are you okay?\N{\rCHT}你還好吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:12.05,0:01:14.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,An ambulance is on the way.\N{\rCHT}救護車快到了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.55,0:01:15.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Thank you.\N{\rCHT}謝謝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.56,0:01:24.35,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Is there a name yet?\N{\rCHT}幫他取名字了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:25.56,0:01:27.29,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Elijah.\N{\rCHT}伊萊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.07,0:01:34.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Is he supposed to be crying like this?\N{\rCHT}他這麼哭正常嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:35.57,0:01:36.97,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,May l?\N{\rCHT}我可以抱抱嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.59,0:01:54.45,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Can l have him back?\N{\rCHT}可以還我了嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.59,0:02:01.59,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What happened during the delivery?\N{\rCHT}生產時出了什麼事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.59,0:02:04.39,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Nothing. it was very quick.\N{\rCHT}沒有 產程很快{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.60,0:02:07.55,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The baby just wanted to come right out.\N{\rCHT}這小子想立刻出世{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.55,0:02:08.73,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,There were no problems.\N{\rCHT}一切正常{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.10,0:02:13.04,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Did you drop him?\N{\rCHT}你有摔到他嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.11,0:02:14.73,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What?\N{\rCHT}什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.11,0:02:17.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Did you drop this baby?\N{\rCHT}你摔到他了嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.61,0:02:20.41,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Jesus Christ, no.\N{\rCHT}天啊 沒有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.62,0:02:27.45,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,inform the ambulance that we have a situation.\N{\rCHT}通知救護車有特殊狀況{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.62,0:02:34.82,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I've never seen... this.\N{\rCHT}我從未看過...這種情形{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:36.63,0:02:40.07,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,it appears that your baby has sustained some fractures\N{\rCHT}看來你的孩子多處骨折{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.13,0:02:43.26,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,while inside your uterus.\N{\rCHT}在你子宮內就骨折了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.14,0:02:48.57,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,His arms and his legs are broken.\N{\rCHT}他的手腳都斷了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.53,0:03:16.19,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,\N{\fs17\fn宋體}主演布魯斯·威利斯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.04,0:03:22.70,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,\N{\fs17\fn宋體}主演撒母耳·傑克遜{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.56,0:03:40.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,This is East rail 177.\N{\rCHT}這是東鐵177號列車{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:03:40.56,0:03:43.08,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Next stop, Philadelphia.\N{\rCHT}下一站 費城{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.60,0:04:18.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Are you alone?\N{\rCHT}這裡有人坐嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.10,0:04:21.83,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah.\N{\rCHT}沒有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.83,0:04:22.83,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah.\N{\rCHT}好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.15,0:05:11.09,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Someone left this magazine.\N{\rCHT}這裡有雜誌{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.09,0:05:12.35,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Want to take a look at it?\N{\rCHT}要看嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.65,0:05:14.59,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Can l take a look at that one?\N{\rCHT}我能看那本嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:21.16,0:05:22.49,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Thanks.\N{\rCHT}謝了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.16,0:05:24.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You like sports?\N{\rCHT}你喜歡運動{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.66,0:05:28.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,it's my field. I represent athletes. I'm an agent.\N{\rCHT}這是我的職業 我是經紀人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.17,0:05:33.57,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Are you looking for any male synchronized swimmers?\N{\rCHT}需要男性水上芭蕾舞者嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.67,0:05:35.17,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm thinking about getting into that.\N{\rCHT}我正想跳呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:35.17,0:05:37.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Is that right?\N{\rCHT}你說真的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.68,0:05:41.68,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm afraid of water.\N{\rCHT}我怕水{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.68,0:05:43.84,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Think that's a problem?\N{\rCHT}那會有問題嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.19,0:05:54.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You represent someone in Philadelphia?\N{\rCHT}你去費城出差{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.19,0:05:56.53,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm meeting this player from Temple University.\N{\rCHT}我要去天普大學見一個選手{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.70,0:05:58.63,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,He's a cornerback.\N{\rCHT}他是個角衛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.70,0:06:02.57,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,This kid is 6'1'', 210 pounds.\N{\rCHT}高6英尺1英寸 重210磅{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.70,0:06:04.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,He runs a 40 in 4.3 seconds.\N{\rCHT}他跑40碼只需4.3秒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.70,0:06:06.71,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,He's gonna be a god.\N{\rCHT}他絕對會紅{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.71,0:06:08.43,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Do you like football?\N{\rCHT}喜歡美式足球嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.71,0:06:11.34,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Not really.\N{\rCHT}還好吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.22,0:06:24.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm David Dunn.\N{\rCHT}我是鄧大衛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.72,0:06:27.32,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Kelly.\N{\rCHT}凱莉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.73,0:06:29.25,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hi, nice to meet you.\N{\rCHT}幸會{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.73,0:06:31.56,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hi, nice to meet you.\N{\rCHT}幸會{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.24,0:06:42.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,How long are you gonna be in Philadelphia?\N{\rCHT}你到費城要停留多久{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.25,0:06:51.75,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm married.\N{\rCHT}我結婚了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.75,0:06:53.05,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Great.\N{\rCHT}真好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.25,0:06:54.58,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm sorry.\N{\rCHT}抱歉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.75,0:06:56.85,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What are you Talking about?\N{\rCHT}你在說什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.26,0:07:03.23,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l think you misunderstood.\N{\rCHT}我想你誤會了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.26,0:07:05.16,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What l was, uh...\N{\rCHT}我剛才...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.76,0:07:07.49,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,saying\N{\rCHT}是說...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.27,0:07:12.67,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l know. l think I'm going to find another seat.\N{\rCHT}我想我換個座位好了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.77,0:07:15.87,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l... L didn't mean, uh...\N{\rCHT}我無意...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.88,0:08:56.43,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's What he fail to realize.\N{\rCHT}這就是他沒有意識到的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.51,0:08:58.43,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I look classy, not trashy.\N{\rCHT}我看起來是優雅 不是垃圾{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.51,0:08:59.89,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I look classy, too.\N{\rCHT}我看起來也很優雅{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.97,0:09:03.35,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What about me? Don't l look classy?\N{\rCHT}那我呢 我不優雅嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.43,0:09:05.85,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,But I'm afraid you forgot...this!\N{\rCHT}但是恐怕你忘了這個{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.94,0:09:07.15,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Andthis!\N{\rCHT}還有這個{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.23,0:09:10.11,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Where has you been, Banana?\N{\rCHT}你到哪裡去了 香蕉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.19,0:09:12.53,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Now I've got you, Weasel.\N{\rCHT}我抓到你了 黃鼠狼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.89,0:09:14.39,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Some cars Are still on fire,\N{\rCHT}有些車廂仍在燃燒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.39,0:09:16.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and the debris is everywhere.\N{\rCHT}殘骸四散{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.40,0:09:19.33,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We are not sure at this time\N{\rCHT}此時我們無法確定{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.40,0:09:21.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,how rescue personnel Will be able to get on scene at all.\N{\rCHT}救援人員能到達現場{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.90,0:09:23.39,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Second Lf you're just tuning in,\N{\rCHT}您若是剛轉到這個頻道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.40,0:09:24.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,East rail train number 177\N{\rCHT}東鐵177列車{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:24.98,0:09:26.56,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,has derailed just outside Philadelphia.\N{\rCHT}剛剛在費城脫軌{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.90,0:09:29.37,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And We're bringing you live coverage from Skycam 4.\N{\rCHT}請收看來自現場的報導{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.41,0:09:31.91,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yes, that appears to be a rescue ambulance,\N{\rCHT}是的 有一輛救護車來到{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.91,0:09:33.28,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and there are more behind it.\N{\rCHT}我還看得到後面還有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.28,0:09:34.34,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l can see on the access road.\N{\rCHT}更多輛都在路上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.91,0:09:38.07,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l don't know how close they're gonna be able to get, David.\N{\rCHT}不知他們能多接近現場 大衛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.07,0:09:39.92,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,These are Woods and, uh, trees.\N{\rCHT}他們進去了 這裡都是木頭 樹{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.92,0:09:42.85,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Uh, it's gonna be a very difficult? rescue effort...\N{\rCHT}這將是個艱困的救援任務吧 救援資源...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.43,0:09:50.33,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,\N{\fs17\fn宋體}爸坐東鐵177列車{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:16.72,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hi. I'm Dr Dubin.\N{\rCHT}我是杜醫生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:17.25,0:10:19.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You're in the emergency room in the\N{\rCHT}這裡是費城市立{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.18,0:10:20.55,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Philadelphia City Hospital.\N{\rCHT}醫院急診室{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.26,0:10:23.28,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You were in a serious accident.\N{\rCHT}你剛遭遇一場嚴重意外{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.26,0:10:25.69,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Look at me.\N{\rCHT}看著我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.76,0:10:28.36,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,How are you feeling?\N{\rCHT}你感覺如何{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.27,0:10:31.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay.\N{\rCHT}還好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.77,0:10:32.76,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Good.\N{\rCHT}很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.77,0:10:35.07,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm going to ask you some questions.\N{\rCHT}我要問你一些問題{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.27,0:10:36.96,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Have you ever had any heart\N{\rCHT}你過去有氣喘{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.96,0:10:38.64,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,or asthma problems in the past?\N{\rCHT}或心臟疾病嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.28,0:10:40.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No.\N{\rCHT}沒有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.78,0:10:43.61,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Kidney or renal problems?\N{\rCHT}腎臟或結石的毛病{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.78,0:10:44.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No.\N{\rCHT}沒有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.78,0:10:46.44,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Any allergies?\N{\rCHT}過敏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.29,0:10:49.81,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No.\N{\rCHT}沒有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.29,0:10:57.85,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Where were you sitting on the train?\N{\rCHT}你在車上坐哪裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.30,0:11:02.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Against the window.\N{\rCHT}靠窗{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:02.80,0:11:05.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,in the passenger car?\N{\rCHT}在客車車廂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.30,0:11:08.17,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah.\N{\rCHT}對{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.31,0:11:12.17,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Where are the other passengers?\N{\rCHT}其他旅客呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.31,0:11:14.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Was your family travelling with you?\N{\rCHT}你有家人同行嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.81,0:11:18.71,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No.\N{\rCHT}沒有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.82,0:11:22.25,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Did you get up from your seat?\N{\rCHT}你有離開座位嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.32,0:11:31.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Are you certain you were in the passenger car?\N{\rCHT}你確定你當時在客車車廂{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.83,0:11:37.99,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yes.\N{\rCHT}是的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.34,0:11:47.85,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Why are you looking at me like that?\N{\rCHT}你幹什麼那樣看著我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.85,0:11:52.68,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Your train derailed. Some kind of malfunction.\N{\rCHT}你坐的火車出軌 機械故障{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:55.72,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,They only found 2 people alive so far.\N{\rCHT}目前只有兩人生還{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.85,0:11:58.65,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You and this man.\N{\rCHT}你和這個人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.36,0:12:02.37,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,His skull Was cracked open\N{\rCHT}他腦殼破裂{\r}
