Dialogue: 0,0:25:29.41,0:25:31.61,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The thing to notice about this piece,\N{\rCHT}這幅畫值得注意的是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:31.92,0:25:35.91,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,the thing that makes it very, very special\N{\rCHT}讓它之所以與眾不同的地方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:35.92,0:25:38.92,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,is its realistic depiction of its figures.\N{\rCHT}就是寫實的人物描繪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:38.92,0:25:40.84,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,When the characters Reached the magazine,\N{\rCHT}那些人物登上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.84,0:25:43.09,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,they Were exaggerated...\N{\rCHT}雜誌時被誇大了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.43,0:25:45.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,a sal Ways happens.\N{\rCHT}事情一向如此{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.93,0:25:50.42,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,This is vintage.\N{\rCHT}這是幅傑作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:25:59.44,0:26:01.81,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Well... wrap it up.\N{\rCHT}好 包起來 我買了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:01.95,0:26:05.28,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You've made a considerably wise decision.\N{\rCHT}你的決定是睿智的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:10.32,0:26:12.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Well, my kid's gonna go berserk.\N{\rCHT}我的小孩會高興死的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:15.33,0:26:16.79,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Once again, please?\N{\rCHT}什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:17.46,0:26:20.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,My son Jeb it's a gift for him.\N{\rCHT}我兒子傑伯 這是送給他的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.46,0:26:22.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,How old is Jeb?\N{\rCHT}傑伯幾歲了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:22.97,0:26:25.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,He's 4.\N{\rCHT}四歲{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:26.34,0:26:27.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No.\N{\rCHT}不{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.84,0:26:32.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No, no, no, no, no.\N{\rCHT}不...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.84,0:26:37.28,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You need to go. Now.\N{\rCHT}請你走吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.85,0:26:39.91,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What'd l say?\N{\rCHT}我說錯什麼了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:40.35,0:26:43.25,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Do you see any Teletubbies in here?\N{\rCHT}我這裡有天線寶寶嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.85,0:26:45.63,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Do you see a slender plastic tag\N{\rCHT}你有看到我衣服上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:45.63,0:26:47.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,clipped to my shirt with my name printed on it?\N{\rCHT}別了寫有我名字的塑膠標籤嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:47.86,0:26:49.42,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Did you see a little Asian child\N{\rCHT}你有看到我這裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:49.42,0:26:50.99,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,with a blank expression sitting outside\N{\rCHT}有投幣就會唱歌{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:51.36,0:26:53.19,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,in a mechanical helicopter\N{\rCHT}還能載個亞洲小孩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:53.19,0:26:54.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,that shakes when you put quarters in it?\N{\rCHT}轉動的直升機嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.86,0:26:56.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No?\N{\rCHT}沒有吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:56.37,0:26:58.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Well, that's what you see at a toy store,\N{\rCHT}那是玩具店才有的東西{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:26:58.87,0:27:00.37,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and you must think you're in a toy store,\N{\rCHT}你一定以為你進了玩具店{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:00.37,0:27:04.24,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,because you're here shopping for an infant named Jeb.\N{\rCHT}因為你要買東西送你的小鬼傑伯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:04.37,0:27:07.31,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Now, one of us has made a gross error\N{\rCHT}我們之中有人弄錯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:07.38,0:27:10.64,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and wasted the other person's valuable time.\N{\rCHT}浪費了彼此寶貴的時間{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:10.88,0:27:12.87,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,This is an art gallery, my friend,\N{\rCHT}這裡是藝廊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:12.88,0:27:16.51,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and this... is a piece of art.\N{\rCHT}而這是...一件藝術品{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:16.89,0:27:21.55,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,\N{\fs17\fn宋體}限量珍藏{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.90,0:27:34.03,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We're by appointment only.\N{\rCHT}我們只接待預約顧客{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.91,0:27:37.41,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l got a card from this store.\N{\rCHT}我收到貴店的卡片{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.41,0:27:39.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Congratulations, you have a mailbox.\N{\rCHT}恭喜 你有一個信箱{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.41,0:27:41.84,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The exhibition isn't for 2 weeks.\N{\rCHT}展覽已經過了兩周了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:42.41,0:27:46.01,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,This one was under the windshield wiper of my car.\N{\rCHT}這張是夾在我車子擋風玻璃上的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:48.42,0:27:50.92,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,How certain are you that you've never taken ill?\N{\rCHT}你有多少把握自己沒生過病{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:50.92,0:27:53.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,75%\N{\rCHT}百分之七十五{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.43,0:27:58.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Well... that's not certain at all, is it?\N{\rCHT}那還不算很有把握吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.93,0:28:01.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's hole number one.\N{\rCHT}那是第一個問題{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.93,0:28:04.92,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l'm going to be extremely skeptical about all this.\N{\rCHT}我要嚴格檢驗我的理論{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:04.93,0:28:07.53,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,About all What?\N{\rCHT}什麼理論{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:08.44,0:28:10.44,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm assuming you've never been injured.\N{\rCHT}我假定你沒受過傷{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:10.44,0:28:11.44,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Would l be wrong in that assumption?\N{\rCHT}我沒說錯吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.44,0:28:13.81,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Dad's been injured.\N{\rCHT}我爸爸受過傷{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:14.94,0:28:17.81,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Is the child correct?\N{\rCHT}這孩子說得對嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.95,0:28:19.47,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yes, sir.\N{\rCHT}是的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.95,0:28:22.04,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,in college, l was in a car accident.\N{\rCHT}我念大學時出過車禍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:22.45,0:28:23.92,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Was It serious?\N{\rCHT}嚴重嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.95,0:28:26.92,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,He couldn't play football any more.\N{\rCHT}他後來就不能打足球了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:27.46,0:28:30.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's hole number2.\N{\rCHT}那是第二個問號{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:30.96,0:28:33.05,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's a big one.\N{\rCHT}很大的問號{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:36.47,0:28:38.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Mr Price, can we talk about the note\N{\rCHT}談談你留在{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.12,0:28:40.43,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,that you left on my car?\N{\rCHT}我車上的卡片吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:40.47,0:28:43.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I've studied the form of comics intimately.\N{\rCHT}我仔細的研究過漫畫{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:43.97,0:28:46.13,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I've spent a third of my life in a hospital bed\N{\rCHT}我三分之一的人生都在住院{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:46.48,0:28:49.45,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,with nothing else to do but read.\N{\rCHT}住院時只能看書{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:49.48,0:28:52.35,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l believe comics are our last link\N{\rCHT}我相信漫畫與古代{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:52.48,0:28:54.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,to an ancient way of passing on history.\N{\rCHT}傳承歷史的方法有所連結{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:54.98,0:28:57.08,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The Egyptians drew on the walls.\N{\rCHT}埃及人在壁上作畫{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:57.49,0:28:59.56,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Countries all over the world\N{\rCHT}全世界的國家仍以{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:28:59.56,0:29:01.89,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,still pass on knowledge through pictorial forms.\N{\rCHT}繪畫的形式傳承知識{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:01.99,0:29:03.99,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l believe comics are a form of history\N{\rCHT}漫畫是歷史的一種形式{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.99,0:29:07.59,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,that someone somewhere felt or experienced.\N{\rCHT}描繪某人的感覺或經驗{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.00,0:29:08.91,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Then, of course, those experiences and that history\N{\rCHT}然後 理所當然的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:08.91,0:29:10.97,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,got chewed up in the commercial machine,\N{\rCHT}那經驗和歷史被商業機器吞噬{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:11.07,0:29:13.37,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,got jazzed up, made titillating,\N{\rCHT}過度包裝 刺激感官{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:13.50,0:29:17.51,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,cartooned for the sale rack.\N{\rCHT}被拍成卡通四處銷售{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.51,0:29:20.94,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,This city has seen its share Of disasters.\N{\rCHT}這城市發生過許多悲劇{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:21.01,0:29:23.44,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l watched the aftermath of that plane crash.\N{\rCHT}我看過飛機墜毀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:23.51,0:29:26.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l watched the carnage of the hotel fire.\N{\rCHT}旅館大火{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:26.02,0:29:28.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l watched the news waiting to hear\N{\rCHT}我看著新聞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:28.06,0:29:30.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,a very specific combination of words,\N{\rCHT}等待一連串特別的字句{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:31.52,0:29:33.99,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,but they never came.\N{\rCHT}但我從未聽見過{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:34.02,0:29:37.53,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Then one day l saw a news story about a train accident,\N{\rCHT}有天我看到火車意外的報導{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.53,0:29:39.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and l heard them.\N{\rCHT}我終於聽見了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:39.53,0:29:41.69,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,There is a sole survivor,\N{\rCHT}事故中只有一位生還者{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.03,0:29:45.13,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and he is miraculously unharmed.\N{\rCHT}他奇跡似地毫髮無傷{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.04,0:29:51.44,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l have something called osteogenesis imperfecta.\N{\rCHT}我患了延遲性骨發生不全{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:51.54,0:29:53.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,lt's a genetic disorder.\N{\rCHT}這是遺傳病{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:54.04,0:29:56.01,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l don't make a particular protein very Well,\N{\rCHT}我無法製造某種蛋白質{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:56.05,0:29:58.55,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and it makes my bones very low in density.\N{\rCHT}所以我的骨質疏鬆{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:29:58.55,0:30:00.71,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Very easy to break.\N{\rCHT}很容易骨折{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.05,0:30:03.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I've had 54 breaks in my life,\N{\rCHT}我骨折過54次{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:03.55,0:30:06.56,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and l have the tamest version of this disorder,\N{\rCHT}我的情況是最輕微的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:06.56,0:30:08.29,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,type one.\N{\rCHT}第一型{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:08.56,0:30:12.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,There are type2, type3, type 4.\N{\rCHT}還有第二 第三 第四型{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:12.06,0:30:15.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Type 4 don't last very long.\N{\rCHT}第四型都活不久{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:15.57,0:30:18.53,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So that's how it popped into my head.\N{\rCHT}所以我才會有這個想法{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:19.07,0:30:21.56,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,lf there is someone like me in the world,\N{\rCHT}若世上有人跟我一樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.57,0:30:23.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and I'm at one end of the spectrum,\N{\rCHT}我在極端值的一端{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:24.07,0:30:26.27,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,couldn't there be someone else\N{\rCHT}會不會有人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.28,0:30:28.48,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,the opposite of me at the other end?\N{\rCHT}是在另一端{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.58,0:30:30.95,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Someone who doesn't get sick,\N{\rCHT}一個不生病{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:30.95,0:30:32.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,who doesn't get hurt like the rest of us?\N{\rCHT}不會受傷的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.08,0:30:36.95,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And he probably doesn't even know it.\N{\rCHT}而他也許根本不自知{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:37.09,0:30:42.05,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The kind of person these stories are about.\N{\rCHT}這些故事裡所描繪的那種人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.09,0:30:46.93,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,A person put here to protect the rest of us.\N{\rCHT}一個能夠保護我們的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:47.60,0:30:49.59,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,To guard us.\N{\rCHT}護衛我們的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:52.10,0:30:53.09,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You think my dad's a real\N{\rCHT}你想我爸是...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:53.10,0:30:56.44,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l don't think anything right now.\N{\rCHT}我什麼都沒想{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:56.61,0:30:59.07,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,lt's apossibility\N{\rCHT}有這個可能性{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:30:59.11,0:31:02.08,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,one With many holes.\N{\rCHT}有許多問號{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:04.61,0:31:08.05,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,joseph, don't take another sip of that water.\N{\rCHT}喬瑟 別再喝那杯水{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:10.62,0:31:12.09,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Go throw it in the trash.\N{\rCHT}把它扔掉{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.12,0:31:12.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,But, Dad\N{\rCHT}但是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:12.62,0:31:15.39,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Do it now, please.\N{\rCHT}快去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:24.13,0:31:27.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l see guys like you All the time in my Work.\N{\rCHT}我工作時看過太多你這種人了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:28.14,0:31:31.57,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You find someone you want to take advantage of,\N{\rCHT}你們想占人便宜{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:31.64,0:31:34.97,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,you tell them a fantastic story,\N{\rCHT}就告訴人們一個奇特的故事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:35.14,0:31:38.05,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and somewhere in there you say it\N{\rCHT}而你們心裡想的是{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:38.15,0:31:41.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l just need your credit card number\N{\rCHT}我只要你的信用卡號碼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:41.15,0:31:44.05,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,a small down payment\N{\rCHT}一小筆頭款{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:45.66,0:31:46.97,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,This morning was the first morning\N{\rCHT}今天是我第一次{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.97,0:31:48.43,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,that l could remember\N{\rCHT}早晨起床時{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:48.43,0:31:49.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,that l didn't open my eyes and feel\N{\rCHT}不會感覺到{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:52.66,0:31:55.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,sadness.\N{\rCHT}悲傷{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:31:58.17,0:32:00.24,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l thought the person that wrote that note\N{\rCHT}我以為留言的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:00.25,0:32:01.73,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,had an answer for me.\N{\rCHT}會給我答案{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:08.68,0:32:10.67,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l'm gonna leave now.\N{\rCHT}我要走了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.68,0:32:13.58,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Good luck with your exhibition.\N{\rCHT}祝展覽順利{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:13.68,0:32:16.05,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So, what kind of job do you have, David?\N{\rCHT}你是做什麼的 大衛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.36,0:32:18.49,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You said you've met guys like me in your work.\N{\rCHT}你說你看過很多像我一樣的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.57,0:32:20.32,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What exactly is it that you do?\N{\rCHT}你到底是做什麼的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:20.69,0:32:23.19,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l work at the University Stadium.\N{\rCHT}我在大學體育場工作{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:23.19,0:32:25.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm a security guard.\N{\rCHT}我是警衛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.77,0:32:33.17,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,\N{\fs17\fn宋體}車事故唯一生還者是本地人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:33:49.08,0:33:51.10,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,\N{\fs17\fn宋體}戰士隊邁向冠軍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.73,0:34:09.93,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,\N{\fs17\fn宋體}本地足球明星在重大車禍中受傷{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.24,0:34:16.30,Default,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,\N{\fs17\fn宋體}火車事故唯一生還者是本地人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.90,0:34:46.39,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I've come to a decision.\N{\rCHT}我做了一個決定{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:46.76,0:34:47.89,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okey\N{\rCHT}你說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:49.41,0:34:51.87,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l just want to ask you something, okay?\N{\rCHT}我想問你一件事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.91,0:34:55.34,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And you can be totally honest.\N{\rCHT}你要誠實回答{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:55.41,0:34:58.94,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm prepared for any answer,\N{\rCHT}我已準備面對任何答案{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:34:58.94,0:35:00.11,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and it won't affect me.\N{\rCHT}不受影響{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:01.42,0:35:04.28,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Have you been with anyone?\N{\rCHT}你有跟別人交往過嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:04.42,0:35:06.65,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l mean, since we've been having problems.\N{\rCHT}就打我們出問題之後{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:06.92,0:35:09.55,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The answer won't affect me.\N{\rCHT}你的答案不會影響我的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.93,0:35:13.36,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l just need to know, you know?\N{\rCHT}我只是需要知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:13.43,0:35:17.49,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,it won't affect me either way.\N{\rCHT}不管怎樣都影響不了我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:18.94,0:35:21.03,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No.\N{\rCHT}沒有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.95,0:35:32.71,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Sorry, David. Sorry.\N{\rCHT}抱歉 大衛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:36.45,0:35:38.72,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Anyway...\N{\rCHT}總之...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:38.96,0:35:41.58,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,my decision is...\N{\rCHT}我的決定是...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.96,0:35:46.79,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,that l want to start again.\N{\rCHT}我想再來一次{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.47,0:35:53.37,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That l want it to be like it was in the beginning.\N{\rCHT}我想一切再從頭開始{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.97,0:36:00.91,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And it's a big deal that you walked away from that train.\N{\rCHT}你的生還意義重大{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:01.98,0:36:05.21,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l feel like it's a second chance.\N{\rCHT}我覺得那是第二次的機會{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.49,0:36:13.79,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And if you feel like asking me out sometime,\N{\rCHT}你若想約我出去什麼的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.99,0:36:16.08,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,it'd be okay.\N{\rCHT}沒問題{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.04,0:36:35.27,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Go for Dunn.\N{\rCHT}我是小鄧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:35.55,0:36:36.55,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It's Jenkins.\N{\rCHT}我是傑金{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.55,0:36:39.45,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Look, We got a guy over at gate 17C With a bogus ticket.\N{\rCHT}17C入口有人持假票{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:39.55,0:36:42.71,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Say she knows you. He Won't tell me his name.\N{\rCHT}他說認識你 不肯透露姓名{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.05,0:36:45.95,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What's he look like?\N{\rCHT}他長什麼樣子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:46.56,0:36:47.89,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Why is it, do you think,\N{\rCHT}為什麼這世界上{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.89,0:36:49.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,that of all the professions in the world,\N{\rCHT}這麼多職業 你為什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:49.46,0:36:50.99,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,you chose protection?\N{\rCHT}要選擇安保{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:53.56,0:36:54.81,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You are a very strange man.\N{\rCHT}你真的很怪{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:54.81,0:36:56.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You could have been a tax accountant.\N{\rCHT}你可以當一個會計師{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:56.31,0:36:57.43,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You could have owned your own gym.\N{\rCHT}你可以擁有自己的健身房{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:57.52,0:36:59.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You could've opened a chain of restaurants.\N{\rCHT}你可以開一個連鎖餐廳{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.10,0:37:01.44,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You could've done one of 1 0,000 things,\N{\rCHT}你本可以做了成千上萬件有意義的事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:01.52,0:37:05.58,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,but in the end, you chose to protect people.\N{\rCHT}但最後 你選擇了保護人們{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.58,0:37:07.37,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You made that decision,\N{\rCHT}你做了那個決定{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.58,0:37:11.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and l find that very, very interesting.\N{\rCHT}而我覺得相當有趣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.58,0:37:14.64,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Now all l need is your credit card number.\N{\rCHT}現在我要你的信用卡號碼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:15.59,0:37:18.28,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That last part was a joke.\N{\rCHT}最後一句是開玩笑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.72,0:37:23.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You're a big sports fan, are you?\N{\rCHT}你是運動迷嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:23.73,0:37:26.29,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,it's starting to intrigue me.\N{\rCHT}我開始對運動有興趣了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:27.83,0:37:30.99,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,it gets heaviest 10 minutes before kick off.\N{\rCHT}開場前十分鐘最擠{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:54.53,0:37:55.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,just give me a minute.\N{\rCHT}等我一分鐘{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.74,0:37:56.95,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,ls there a problem?\N{\rCHT}有問題嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.70,0:38:01.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The tall guy in the camouflage jacket.\N{\rCHT}那個穿迷彩夾克的高個子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.86,0:38:04.59,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Sometimes people carry weapons in here,\N{\rCHT}有時人們喝多了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.87,0:38:06.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and they drink too much.\N{\rCHT}帶了武器過來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.87,0:38:08.87,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,lf the team's not doing good,\N{\rCHT}要是球隊表現不好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:08.87,0:38:11.03,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,bad things can happen.\N{\rCHT}就會出事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.87,0:38:13.94,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We do pat downs Of the crowd\N{\rCHT}我們搜身好嚇跑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:13.94,0:38:15.71,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,to discourage people from carrying.\N{\rCHT}那些攜械的人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:16.38,0:38:19.11,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,lf he's carrying, he'll step out of line.\N{\rCHT}要是他有攜械 他會走出隊伍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.17,0:38:48.08,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l got you a seat up in the yellow section.\N{\rCHT}我安排你坐黃區{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.18,0:38:49.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,it's in the nosebleeds,\N{\rCHT}那區地勢最高{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:49.81,0:38:51.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,but at least you won't get spit on.\N{\rCHT}沒人會吐你口水{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.18,0:38:53.68,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,All right.\N{\rCHT}好了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.68,0:38:55.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,How'd you know that guy you bumped\N{\rCHT}你怎會知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.66,0:38:57.64,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,was carrying a weapon?\N{\rCHT}那傢伙攜械{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.19,0:39:01.45,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l don't know.\N{\rCHT}我不知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:01.69,0:39:06.13,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Maybe it was that camouflage army jacket he was wearing.\N{\rCHT}也許是因為他穿著野戰外套吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.20,0:39:08.89,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Those guys like to carry hunting knives and stuff for show.\N{\rCHT}那種人都喜歡帶刀帶槍的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:09.20,0:39:12.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You thought he was carrying a knife?\N{\rCHT}你認為他身上有刀子{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.70,0:39:14.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l thought he was carrying something, yeah.\N{\rCHT}我認為他帶了傢伙{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:14.20,0:39:16.87,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,But not a knife.\N{\rCHT}但不是一把刀{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.21,0:39:21.07,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l got a...\N{\rCHT}我看到...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:21.21,0:39:21.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,picture ofa silver gun with a black grip\N{\rCHT}一幅畫面{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:22.21,0:39:26.72,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,tucked in his pants.\N{\rCHT}他腰上有把黑柄的銀色手槍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:26.72,0:39:30.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You know, like on TV.\N{\rCHT}就跟電視上演的一樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:30.22,0:39:33.15,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You have good instincts for things like that?\N{\rCHT}你對那種事直覺很准嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:33.72,0:39:34.72,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Like what?\N{\rCHT}什麼事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.72,0:39:38.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Knowing when people have done something wrong.\N{\rCHT}知道人們做了不對的事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.23,0:39:41.36,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah.\N{\rCHT}對{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:41.73,0:39:44.76,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Have you ever tried to develop it?\N{\rCHT}有試過開發這能力嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:45.74,0:39:46.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l don't know what you're asking me.\N{\rCHT}我不懂你在說什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:46.74,0:39:49.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Your skill.\N{\rCHT}你的技巧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:49.74,0:39:51.49,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Look, l got to be down on the sidelines during the game.\N{\rCHT}比賽時我要在場邊{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:51.49,0:39:53.23,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You can get to your seat right down here\N{\rCHT}你可以到你的座位去了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.24,0:39:56.68,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Characters in comics are often attributed special powers\N{\rCHT}漫畫人物通常都有特異功能{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.75,0:40:01.01,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,invisibility, X Ray vision, things of that sort.\N{\rCHT}隱形 透視之類的能力{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.25,0:40:03.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay.\N{\rCHT}好了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:03.75,0:40:05.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l don't want to play this game any more.\N{\rCHT}我不想再談這個了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:05.76,0:40:08.49,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,it's an exaggeration ofthe truth.\N{\rCHT}那是現實的誇張表現{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:08.76,0:40:12.33,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Maybe it's based on something\N{\rCHT}也許那就像是種{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:12.33,0:40:13.35,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,as simple as instinct.\N{\rCHT}直覺{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:14.26,0:40:15.77,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,But he might not have been carrying anything.\N{\rCHT}他也許什麼也沒帶{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:15.77,0:40:17.67,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,But he might have been carrying a silver gun\N{\rCHT}但是他的腰間也許{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:17.67,0:40:19.57,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,with a black grip tucked in his pants.\N{\rCHT}真有把黑柄銀手槍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.77,0:40:20.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Dunn.\N{\rCHT}小鄧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.77,0:40:23.47,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l gotta go.\N{\rCHT}我得走了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:24.77,0:40:27.04,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah, l know. I'll be right down.\N{\rCHT}知道了 我馬上下來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:27.28,0:40:29.07,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,One last question.\N{\rCHT}最後一個問題{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:29.28,0:40:30.61,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What?\N{\rCHT}說吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:30.78,0:40:32.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That car accident you were in.\N{\rCHT}你上次出的車禍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:32.78,0:40:35.65,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Was there anyone else involved?\N{\rCHT}當時還有別人嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.29,0:40:37.72,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yeah.\N{\rCHT}有{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:37.72,0:40:39.28,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,My wife Audrey.\N{\rCHT}我太太{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:39.28,0:40:42.92,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,She was in the car with me.\N{\rCHT}她跟我一起{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.79,0:40:47.09,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Have a good life, Elijah.\N{\rCHT}祝你愉快{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.16,0:40:49.41,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Next time, try to buy your tickets\N{\rCHT}下次別跟著{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.50,0:40:51.21,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,at an authorized sales location.\N{\rCHT}買黃牛票了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:54.21,0:40:55.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm on my way.\N{\rCHT}我馬上到{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:40:59.44,0:41:01.91,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,...into the investigation of train 177\N{\rCHT}177列車事故調查{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:01.94,0:41:04.68,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,being conducted at the East rail holding Warehouses.\N{\rCHT}在東鐵庫房展開{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.68,0:41:07.56,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The city council Has stepped up plans to pass a bill...\N{\rCHT}市議會計畫通過一項法案{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.23,0:41:11.69,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,requiring higher standards for inspection and maintenance\N{\rCHT}要求對大費城地區的鐵路{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.77,0:41:13.44,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,of all rail transportation in Philadelphia\N{\rCHT}運輸執行更高的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.52,0:41:14.73,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and its outlying districts.\N{\rCHT}檢驗及維修標準{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.47,0:41:25.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hold up a second!\N{\rCHT}等一等{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:42:20.26,0:42:23.42,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l just Want to ask you something.\N{\rCHT}我只想問你一個問題{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:32.63,0:43:33.99,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Dad!\N{\rCHT}爸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:34.13,0:43:35.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hey, Dad!\N{\rCHT}爸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:42.50,0:43:43.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Dad!\N{\rCHT}爸{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:53.72,0:43:56.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,joseph, do you know how mad your mother would be\N{\rCHT}約瑟夫 你媽要是知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:57.06,0:43:59.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,if she knew you were playing football?\N{\rCHT}你玩足球就完了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:43:59.02,0:44:00.85,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Are you gonna tell?\N{\rCHT}你不會說吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:02.02,0:44:03.89,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You want to play last of the downs?\N{\rCHT}來打最後一輪進攻吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:04.03,0:44:05.36,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We got a big guy like you.\N{\rCHT}我們隊上有好手{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:05.53,0:44:07.83,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You could play on opposite sides.\N{\rCHT}你可以加入對方{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:08.03,0:44:09.53,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,He's Potter's cousin.\N{\rCHT}他是考波特{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:09.53,0:44:12.09,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,He's starting cornerback at Temple University.\N{\rCHT}天普大學的先發角衛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:12.53,0:44:14.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,He's going pro in the draft.\N{\rCHT}他要參加選秀會{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:14.54,0:44:17.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,They say he can run the 40 in 4.3 seconds.\N{\rCHT}聽說他40碼只跑4.3秒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:18.04,0:44:20.01,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I've heard.\N{\rCHT}我聽說過了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:20.04,0:44:22.01,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You can beat him, Dad.\N{\rCHT}你可以打敗他的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:22.04,0:44:22.81,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's beat'em.\N{\rCHT}去痛宰他們吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:23.05,0:44:24.54,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm gonna go in.\N{\rCHT}我要進屋去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:24.55,0:44:27.05,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,just play one set of downs. l told them you were great.\N{\rCHT}就打一輪 我說過你很行的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:27.05,0:44:27.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Why'd you do that?\N{\rCHT}你為何那樣說{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:28.05,0:44:29.35,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,just one.\N{\rCHT}一輪就好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:29.55,0:44:31.55,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm gonna go in. I've got some things to do.\N{\rCHT}我要進屋 我有事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:31.55,0:44:32.75,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What things?\N{\rCHT}什麼事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:33.06,0:44:34.52,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm gonna work out.\N{\rCHT}我要健身{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:34.56,0:44:35.35,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'll help you.\N{\rCHT}我幫你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:35.56,0:44:36.55,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l don't need\N{\rCHT}不需要{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:36.56,0:44:37.88,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l can't play, guys!\N{\rCHT}我不能玩了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.88,0:44:40.26,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm working out with my dad!\N{\rCHT}我要幫我爸健身{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:01.45,0:45:03.75,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,How much did you put on there?\N{\rCHT}你加多重{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:12.46,0:45:15.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You put too much. That's 250 pounds.\N{\rCHT}太重了 250磅{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:16.47,0:45:19.16,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,How much can you lift?\N{\rCHT}你能舉多重{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:19.97,0:45:22.53,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's the most l ever lifted.\N{\rCHT}這是我舉過最重的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:24.47,0:45:27.27,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That could've been dangerous, Joseph.\N{\rCHT}這很危險的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.48,0:45:28.39,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Why don't you go upstairs now\N{\rCHT}你上樓去吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:28.39,0:45:29.48,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and let me finish up, okay?\N{\rCHT}我自己練{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:29.48,0:45:32.28,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'll take it off. I'll help you right.\N{\rCHT}我拿掉重量 好好幫你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:37.49,0:45:40.85,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You think you could have beaten up Bruce Lee?\N{\rCHT}你想你能打敗李小龍嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:40.99,0:45:42.92,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No.\N{\rCHT}不能{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:42.99,0:45:45.36,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l mean, if you knew karate.\N{\rCHT}我是說 若你會空手道的話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:45.49,0:45:48.16,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No.\N{\rCHT}不能{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:51.50,0:45:52.89,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What if he wasn't allowed to kick,\N{\rCHT}要是他不能踢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:52.89,0:45:54.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and you were really mad at him?\N{\rCHT}你又氣瘋了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:45:54.50,0:45:56.56,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,No, Joseph.\N{\rCHT}不能{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:38.05,0:46:40.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,How much did you take off?\N{\rCHT}你拿掉多少重量{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:42.55,0:46:44.45,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l lied.\N{\rCHT}我騙你的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:47.56,0:46:49.72,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You added?\N{\rCHT}你加重量{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:46:57.57,0:46:59.83,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,How much is it?\N{\rCHT}總共多重{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:01.07,0:47:03.83,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,270 pounds.\N{\rCHT}270磅{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:06.58,0:47:08.94,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Let's put more.\N{\rCHT}再加點重量{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:12.08,0:47:13.71,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay.\N{\rCHT}好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:17.59,0:47:18.89,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Why don't you move back a little\N{\rCHT}你退後點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:18.89,0:47:20.85,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,just to be safe, okay?\N{\rCHT}安全第一{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:47:53.12,0:47:55.09,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,More?\N{\rCHT}再加{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.13,0:48:08.39,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You should never do anything like this.\N{\rCHT}你不可以學我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.39,0:48:10.26,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You know that, right?\N{\rCHT}知道嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:12.14,0:48:14.61,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What do you do If something bad happens?\N{\rCHT}要是出事你要怎麼辦{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:14.64,0:48:16.51,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Get Mom.\N{\rCHT}去找媽{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:17.15,0:48:18.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Right.\N{\rCHT}沒錯{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.18,0:48:56.08,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,How much did you put on that time?\N{\rCHT}這回你加了多少{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:00.19,0:49:02.59,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,All of it.\N{\rCHT}全部{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:04.69,0:49:07.25,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What else can we use?\N{\rCHT}還能加什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:33.22,0:49:35.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,How much is it?\N{\rCHT}多重{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:44.23,0:49:46.39,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,How much is it, Dad?\N{\rCHT}總共多重{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:49.24,0:49:51.97,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,About 350 pounds.\N{\rCHT}350磅左右{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:49:59.01,0:50:00.92,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Fracture of the fifth Metacarpal of the right hand,\N{\rCHT}右手掌骨折{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:01.01,0:50:02.34,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,as well as multiple fractures\N{\rCHT}第6 7 8根肋骨{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:02.43,0:50:04.30,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,of the sixth, seventh, and eighth ribs.\N{\rCHT}也多數骨折{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.39,0:50:05.68,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The worst of the injury, however,\N{\rCHT}傷的最嚴重的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:05.76,0:50:07.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,was sustained to the right leg\N{\rCHT}是右腳{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:07.26,0:50:09.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,in the form of a spiral fracture.\N{\rCHT}螺旋骨折{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:09.10,0:50:11.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,There were 1 4 breaks.\N{\rCHT}斷了14處{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:11.18,0:50:12.48,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,it simply shattered.\N{\rCHT}完全粉碎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:14.20,0:50:16.70,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,They call me Mr Glass.\N{\rCHT}他們叫我玻璃娃娃{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:16.70,0:50:17.79,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Who does?\N{\rCHT}誰{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:18.20,0:50:20.23,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Kids.\N{\rCHT}孩子們{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:20.70,0:50:22.69,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Are you All right, Mr Price?\N{\rCHT}你還好吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:22.70,0:50:25.07,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Shall l continue?\N{\rCHT}要繼續嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.21,0:50:28.21,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Pins Were placed through out the length of the leg.\N{\rCHT}整只腿已打上鋼釘{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:28.21,0:50:29.59,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The use of a Wheelchair\N{\rCHT}你要以輪椅{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.59,0:50:30.97,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Will be needed For a 2 monthperiod.\N{\rCHT}代步二個月{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:31.21,0:50:34.55,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The use of crutches Will Follow for 12 to 14months.\N{\rCHT}接下來12至14個月用拐杖{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:34.72,0:50:37.01,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Hospital stay Will range from 5 to 8days\N{\rCHT}住院治療5至8天{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:37.22,0:50:40.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,folloWed by 9 to 12 months of physical therapy.\N{\rCHT}其後9至12個月做物理治療{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.22,0:50:42.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Prescribed medication for pain management\N{\rCHT}我給你疼痛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:42.10,0:50:44.35,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Will take the usual forms of morphine drip,\N{\rCHT}控制用一般的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:44.35,0:50:45.85,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,perco cet, darvocet.\N{\rCHT}嗎啡止痛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:57.24,0:50:59.24,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Your 1 0:00 is here.\N{\rCHT}你十點的病人來了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.24,0:51:01.64,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The hospital discharged him this morning.\N{\rCHT}他今早出院{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.75,0:51:05.41,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Thanks.\N{\rCHT}謝謝{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:14.26,0:51:15.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Elijah, right?\N{\rCHT}伊萊 對吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:16.07,0:51:18.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We're gonna prevent any substantial atrophy\N{\rCHT}我們用這來防止你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:18.38,0:51:19.53,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,of your good leg with this,\N{\rCHT}腿部萎縮{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:19.58,0:51:22.41,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and it works your quadriceps.\N{\rCHT}這也能鍛煉你的四頭肌{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:23.08,0:51:25.71,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,How long have you been married?\N{\rCHT}你結婚多久了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:28.08,0:51:29.48,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,12 years.\N{\rCHT}12年{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:29.59,0:51:32.11,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,How'd you get together?\N{\rCHT}你們為何會結婚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:33.59,0:51:35.09,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm a little nervous being here.\N{\rCHT}我有點緊張{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:35.09,0:51:39.03,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l ask too many questions when I'm nervous.\N{\rCHT}我緊張時就愛拼命提問題{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:41.10,0:51:43.36,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,A car accident.\N{\rCHT}一場車禍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:44.10,0:51:47.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Now you're going to have to tell me more.\N{\rCHT}你告訴我更多細節了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:51.11,0:51:53.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,My husband was a star athlete in college,\N{\rCHT}他原是大學足球明星{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.61,0:51:57.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and we were in an accident together.\N{\rCHT}我們發生一場車禍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:57.61,0:51:59.01,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Our car flipped on an icy road,\N{\rCHT}翻車了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.12,0:51:59.86,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and we were both injured,\N{\rCHT}我們受傷{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:51:59.86,0:52:01.55,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and he couldn't play football any more.\N{\rCHT}他無法再打球了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:01.62,0:52:02.51,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And if that hadn't happened,\N{\rCHT}要不是那樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:02.51,0:52:04.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,we probably wouldn't have been together.\N{\rCHT}我們也不會結婚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:04.12,0:52:05.92,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,How so?\N{\rCHT}傷到哪裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:06.12,0:52:08.09,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l think we should talk about your rehab.\N{\rCHT}我們該談你的複健治療{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:08.12,0:52:10.85,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You don't have to answer if you don't want to.\N{\rCHT}不想答就不用答{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:11.63,0:52:16.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So, tell me more about the quad machine.\N{\rCHT}跟我說說那台機器吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:16.63,0:52:21.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,lt prevents atrophy by...\N{\rCHT}它可以預防肌肉萎縮{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:21.14,0:52:24.17,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l couldn't spend my life with someone who played football.\N{\rCHT}我不能跟足球選手共度一生{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:24.17,0:52:25.94,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,it's pretty much that simple.\N{\rCHT}就這麼簡單{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:26.64,0:52:28.27,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And l don't hate the game.\N{\rCHT}我不討厭球賽{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:28.28,0:52:29.91,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l admire the amount of skill it involves.\N{\rCHT}我欣賞包括其中的技能{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:30.15,0:52:31.16,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And like everyone else,\N{\rCHT}跟別人一樣{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:31.16,0:52:32.94,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l was in awe of the way he played it,\N{\rCHT}我一樣覺得他很棒{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:33.15,0:52:37.95,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,but football, in many ways, is the opposite of what l do.\N{\rCHT}但足球跟我的職業背道而馳{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:38.15,0:52:40.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You're rewarded the more you punish your opponent.\N{\rCHT}痛宰對手卻能得到獎賞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:40.66,0:52:42.11,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You know, it's too much about violence,\N{\rCHT}太暴力了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:42.11,0:52:45.03,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and l don't want violence in my life.\N{\rCHT}我不喜歡暴力{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:45.66,0:52:48.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,it's not a thing many people can understand, but...\N{\rCHT}很多人都不能瞭解這點{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:49.17,0:52:50.67,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Anyway,\N{\rCHT}總之...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.09,0:52:52.64,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,fate stepped in with that car accident\N{\rCHT}命運讓我跳過了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:52.76,0:52:54.89,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and took football out other equation.\N{\rCHT}這個足球給我帶來的障礙{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:54.97,0:52:58.48,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,And everyone lived Happily ever after.\N{\rCHT}而且所有人都皆大歡喜{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.68,0:53:01.37,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Sort of.\N{\rCHT}算吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:01.68,0:53:05.11,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What part of David's body Was in jured?\N{\rCHT}大衛傷到哪裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:53:06.18,0:53:08.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Who said my husband's name was David?\N{\rCHT}我沒提過我丈夫叫大衛{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:01.78,0:54:03.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,A 737 crashes on takeoff\N{\rCHT}一架737客機起飛時失事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:03.78,0:54:06.77,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,172 die, no survivors.\N{\rCHT}死了172人 無人生還{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:07.29,0:54:10.29,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,A hotel fire downtown, 211 die,\N{\rCHT}一棟旅館火災 211人死亡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.29,0:54:11.76,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,no survivors.\N{\rCHT}無人生還{\r}
