Dialogue: 0,1:02:56.27,1:02:58.91,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,tucked in the back of his pants.\N{\rCHT}黑柄銀色手槍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:00.19,1:03:03.45,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Were you really injured in that car accident in college?\N{\rCHT}你大學車禍時真的有受傷{\r}
