Dialogue: 0,1:03:05.88,1:03:07.34,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l believe you took the opportunity\N{\rCHT}我認為你藉機結束{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:07.46,1:03:10.13,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,to end your football career, no questions asked.\N{\rCHT}你的足球生涯{\r}
