Dialogue: 0,1:03:35.91,1:03:37.53,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Most guns have a black or silver handle.\N{\rCHT}大多數槍有一個黑色或銀色的把手{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:37.66,1:03:39.62,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l had a 50 50 shot of getting the colour right.\N{\rCHT}我有一個50式手槍正好符合{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:39.74,1:03:40.91,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's not What l Witnessed.\N{\rCHT}那不是我親眼目睹{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:40.99,1:03:43.04,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Stop.\N{\rCHT}夠了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:43.12,1:03:46.38,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Stop messing with my life, Elijah.\N{\rCHT}別再來擾亂我的生活 以利亞{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:46.46,1:03:48.67,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,My son almost shot me last night,\N{\rCHT}我兒子因你的話{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:48.75,1:03:50.21,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,because he wanted to prove you were right.\N{\rCHT}差點對我開槍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:03:50.30,1:03:51.92,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l never said you couldn't be killed.\N{\rCHT}我沒說你有不死之身{\r}
