Dialogue: 0,1:04:10.94,1:04:12.42,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,2 skinny little kids\N{\rCHT}兩個小孩惡作劇{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:12.42,1:04:13.90,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,were fooling around in a pool dunking me,\N{\rCHT}把我扔進水塘裡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:13.99,1:04:15.45,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and l swallowed some water.\N{\rCHT}我喝很多水{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:15.53,1:04:18.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,They didn't know it, and it almost killed me.\N{\rCHT}他們不知道 我差點因此身亡{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:18.91,1:04:21.37,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Heroes don't get killed like that.\N{\rCHT}英雄不會死的如此慘{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:21.45,1:04:23.33,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Normal people do, right?\N{\rCHT}普通人會 對嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:25.29,1:04:29.75,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l don't need to see you any more, okay?\N{\rCHT}我不想再看到你了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:29.84,1:04:32.75,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Please stay away from my family.\N{\rCHT}請離我的家人遠一點{\r}
