Dialogue: 0,1:04:54.63,1:04:57.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You better not be Jacking off\N{\rCHT}你可別邊看小本漫畫{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:04:57.74,1:04:59.13,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,to the Japanese comics, l swear to God.\N{\rCHT}邊打手槍{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:12.15,1:05:15.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Look, man, l didn't know you were in a...\N{\rCHT}我不知道你坐輪椅{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:16.65,1:05:19.32,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,just choose something, all right?\N{\rCHT}總之快點選吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:24.53,1:05:26.93,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,The baby sitter's here.\N{\rCHT}保姆到了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:29.53,1:05:30.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Should we cancel?\N{\rCHT}要取消嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:31.04,1:05:33.27,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm fine.\N{\rCHT}我很好{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:35.54,1:05:38.41,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We can do this another time.\N{\rCHT}我們可以改天再去{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:38.54,1:05:41.03,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't lie.\N{\rCHT}別說謊了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:42.55,1:05:45.91,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm fine. l just got mixed up.\N{\rCHT}我很好 我只是有點困惑{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:05:52.56,1:05:55.89,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,How about we just go for a couple drinks?\N{\rCHT}我們去喝點東西吧{\r}
