Dialogue: 0,1:06:03.82,1:06:05.79,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,All right? You can think about things outside on the sidewalk.\N{\rCHT}你可以在路邊想清楚{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:06:05.82,1:06:09.02,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l got to get some chicken in me, you know what I'm saying?\N{\rCHT}我要去吃點東西{\r}
