Dialogue: 0,1:07:07.52,1:07:09.01,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's it, crackerjack.\N{\rCHT}夠了 怪人{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:09.02,1:07:11.45,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You're going to be sitting your ass in jail now.\N{\rCHT}你等著坐牢吧{\r}
