Dialogue: 0,1:07:33.54,1:07:35.74,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,How much for this one?\N{\rCHT}這本多少錢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:38.46,1:07:39.76,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Rust?\N{\rCHT}鐵銹色{\r}
