Dialogue: 0,1:07:44.47,1:07:49.27,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You know, like... rust coloured paint or wood.\N{\rCHT}那是叫紅褐色{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:49.97,1:07:51.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l didn't know that.\N{\rCHT}我真的不知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:51.48,1:07:56.00,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,mine's still brown.\N{\rCHT}我還是最愛棕色{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:56.48,1:07:57.98,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay, my turn.\N{\rCHT}換我了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:07:57.98,1:08:00.28,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Favourite song?\N{\rCHT}最喜歡的歌曲{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:00.49,1:08:04.49,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Soft and Wet by the Artist Formerly Known as Prince.\N{\rCHT}王子唱的 "柔潤"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:04.49,1:08:06.46,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,what?\N{\rCHT}什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:06.99,1:08:09.65,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,We're supposed to be honest.\N{\rCHT}我們應該要坦誠的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:09.99,1:08:12.50,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Soft and Wet.\N{\rCHT}"柔潤"{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:12.50,1:08:14.66,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's very interesting.\N{\rCHT}真有意思{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:15.00,1:08:17.73,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Okay, my turn.\N{\rCHT}好 換我了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:18.50,1:08:21.84,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,When was the first time... the thought\N{\rCHT}你何時開始想...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:22.01,1:08:26.44,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,popped into your head we might not make it?\N{\rCHT}我們可能無法廝守終身{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:26.51,1:08:28.57,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That's not the game.\N{\rCHT}遊戲不包括這個{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:29.01,1:08:32.85,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,it's the first date. There aren't any rules.\N{\rCHT}這是約會 沒有規則{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:36.02,1:08:37.52,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Don't know for sure.\N{\rCHT}我不確定{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:37.52,1:08:40.05,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Think carefully.\N{\rCHT}仔細想{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:41.03,1:08:42.53,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What about the game?\N{\rCHT}遊戲呢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:42.53,1:08:45.39,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,it's over. l won.\N{\rCHT}結束了 我贏了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:47.03,1:08:48.83,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Look, maybe it wasn't a specific moment.\N{\rCHT}也許不是什麼特定時間{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:49.03,1:08:50.47,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Maybe it was a time\N{\rCHT}也許只是...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:50.54,1:08:53.87,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l had a nightmare one night,\N{\rCHT}有天晚上我做了個惡夢{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:08:54.04,1:09:00.53,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,and... l didn't wake you up, so you could tell me that it was okay.\N{\rCHT}而我沒叫醒你 要你安慰我{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:01.05,1:09:04.21,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l think that was the first time.\N{\rCHT}我想就是打那時候開始的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:05.55,1:09:08.21,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Does that count?\N{\rCHT}那算嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:09.05,1:09:10.99,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,That counts.\N{\rCHT}算{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.06,1:09:19.55,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Do you knowingly keep me and Joseph at a distance?\N{\rCHT}你是故意疏離我和喬瑟{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:26.57,1:09:28.44,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Yes.\N{\rCHT}對{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.07,1:09:31.20,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Why?\N{\rCHT}為什麼{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.08,1:09:35.41,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l don't know.\N{\rCHT}我不知道{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.58,1:09:42.78,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l just don't feel right, Audrey.\N{\rCHT}我就是覺得不對勁{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:43.59,1:09:45.92,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Something's...\N{\rCHT}有事情...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.09,1:09:48.96,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Just not right.\N{\rCHT}不大對勁{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:50.60,1:09:53.60,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Do you resent us, David?\N{\rCHT}你討厭我們嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:53.60,1:09:56.47,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Resent the life you have?\N{\rCHT}你討厭你的生活{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:09:58.10,1:10:01.61,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l mean, there were a lot of other things you could've done after college.\N{\rCHT}大學畢業後你本可以做許多事{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.61,1:10:04.63,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,These were your choices.\N{\rCHT}這些是你選擇的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:09.11,1:10:11.12,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You know, even if it meant we couldn't have been together,\N{\rCHT}就算會讓我們無法廝守{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.12,1:10:14.45,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l never would've wished that injury on you.\N{\rCHT}我也不願你受傷{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.62,1:10:19.06,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,What you could do physically was a gift.\N{\rCHT}你的體能是上天的恩賜{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:19.62,1:10:22.75,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l never would've wished it to go away.\N{\rCHT}我從未希望你失去它{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:24.63,1:10:27.22,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You know that, right?\N{\rCHT}你知道的 對吧{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:30.64,1:10:32.80,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,You had 2 calls afterJoseph went to bed\N{\rCHT}喬瑟上床後有兩通電話找你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:33.14,1:10:36.11,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,One came through while l was on the other line,\N{\rCHT}第一通是我正在通話時插播的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:36.14,1:10:39.87,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,There Was an emergency With my sister.\N{\rCHT}我姐自助燙髮出了點麻煩{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:40.14,1:10:42.01,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Who called through?\N{\rCHT}誰打來的{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:42.15,1:10:45.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,someone from New York,\N{\rCHT}一個人從紐約打來{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:10:45.15,1:10:48.14,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,uh, about a security job. They Want to hire you.\N{\rCHT}說什麼保全工作 你被錄取了{\r}
