Dialogue: 0,1:40:20.12,1:40:22.72,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Do you know What the scariest thing is?\N{\rCHT}知道什麼事最可怕嗎{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:26.13,1:40:29.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,To not know your place in this world,\N{\rCHT}不知道自己歸屬於何處{\r}
