Dialogue: 0,1:40:54.66,1:40:57.09,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,But l found you.\N{\rCHT}但我找到了你{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:40:57.66,1:41:01.96,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,So many sacrifices...\N{\rCHT}犧牲了這麼多人...{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:02.16,1:41:04.10,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,Just to find you.\N{\rCHT}只為了找到你{\r}
