Dialogue: 0,1:41:20.18,1:41:22.88,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,l know who l am.\N{\rCHT}我也知道我是誰了{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:26.69,1:41:28.68,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,I'm not a mistake.\N{\rCHT}我不是個錯誤{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:30.19,1:41:32.18,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,It all makes sense.\N{\rCHT}一切都很合理{\r}
Dialogue: 0,1:41:32.62,1:41:36.08,ENG,NTP,0,0,0,!Effect,In a comic, you know how you can tell who the arch villain's going to be?\N{\rCHT}在漫畫裡 誰會是大魔王呢{\r}
